    "semanticIteration": "one controller-authorized task-attempt slot containing zero or one logical semantic call; deterministic-only work consumes no iteration",
    "logicalSemanticCall": "one budgeted semantic usage event produced by either a live provider invocation or a deterministic replay; fallback and cache reuse never reset the counter",
